hat week.<br>
<br>
She walked over to Kali and smiled softly raising her hand outward in the Amazon peace shake.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yasoo Kali, welcome to Scynthia.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxamznkali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XAmznKali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(10/18/01 10:28:59 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=www.homeotwn.aol.com/xamazonkalix WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A new athelfi</span><hr size=1> She smiled seeing the Queen it was an honor. She held her hand outward and completed the handshake with Alysia.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yasoo Queen Alysia, Its an honor to meet you. and thank you for the Welcoming. Scynthia is beautiful, your a lucky Queen. Or is it Scynthia the one thats lucky?&quot;<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 241<br> <font color=#993300>(10/21/01 11:52:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Scynthia</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled at the words of the new athelfi.<br>
<br>
&quot;No no, I am the one that is lucky. Scynthia is more than anything I ever dreamed of.&quot; She glanced about her lands.<br>
<br>
&quot;Plus, these are the largest lands of the Amazon Nation.&quot; She smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;You'll soon learn the ways of the Scynthian tribes differ greatly from others.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxamznkali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XAmznKali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#993300>(10/21/01 4:51:13 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Scynthia</span><hr size=1> &quot;I know the ways of Scynthia are quite different. Unlike some northern Amazons you respect the gods but don't worship them. That's why I think I'll enjoy this tribe.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 242<br> <font color=#993300>(10/21/01 8:19:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Gods and Mortals and Ancients Oh My!</span><hr size=1> She frowned at the thought of some of the Gods. <br>
<br>
&quot;Yes, we do not worship such things. However, we have our own dieties if you would call them. They are the creators of the Amazon Ways. The first Amazons. We call them the ancients.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxamznkali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XAmznKali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#993300>(10/22/01 6:44:23 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=www.homeotwn.aol.com/xamazonkalix WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gods and Mortals and Ancients Oh My!</span><hr size=1> She smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes the Ancients, my mother wrote a story of them and an evil shamaness named...&quot; <br>
<br>
She thinks a minute.<br>
<br>
&quot;name Alti and another shamaness who tried to harness Alti's power but failed...Her name was Yakut I think.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 244<br> <font color=#993300>(10/22/01 10:38:56 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Alti</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded slightly thinking of the Shamaness. She then smiled at the thought of Yakut. Though she had recieved word of her death . . . she knew her spirit would one day return as they always did.<br>
<br>
She nodded. &quot;Yes, Alti and Yakut. I knew them both personally, however, they are of a different era than we. We come from one that began before them, before alot, some say before even the Titans themselves. We worship those known as the Atmah Cyane, and sometimes Samsara the Great.&quot;<br>
<br>
She wouldn't reveal to the girl that Alysia was Samsara, perhaps another time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxamznkali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XAmznKali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#993300>(10/25/01 5:44:29 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=www.homeotwn.aol.com/xamazonkalix WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Alti</span><hr size=1> &quot;May I ask, I heard you were a goddess as well, how can you be not what you worship?&quot;<br>
<br>
She meant no offense to the Queen, she was just curious of...well EVERYTHING. [lol] <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 245<br> <font color=#993300>(10/26/01 1:33:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Goddess</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;I am what is called a Shamaness, you already know of this naturally. However, I was born an immortal. Long ago before I ever knew what Scynthia was. Upon my Amazon Initiation, I was blessed by the Goddesses Artemis and Athena.&quot;<br>
<br>
She smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;Each gave me a gift, and they blessed me with powers saying that I would be a healer that the amazon nation would never again see. That I would be able to help my athelfi in ways that others could not. They gave me the title of an &quot;Amazon&quot; Goddess. Which differs that from the Olympians.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxamznkali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XAmznKali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#993300>(10/26/01 5:07:27 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=www.homeotwn.aol.com/xamazonkalix WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Goddess</span><hr size=1> Nods understanding.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ohh. Yes I know what a shaman is but just so you know. Well, Queen, I meant no offense to you by my question, I am just curious. I hope you accept my apologies if I have offended you.&quot;<br>
<br>
She shifted as her small saluki dog named Gerfiniwho was a gift from her best friend Nefertiti Princess of Egypt. He sat down and stood still at her side.<br>
<br>
&quot;I have a question, when a Nothern Amazon dies, does she beome an Ancient or is that just the first Amazons who are called the Ancients?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 247<br> <font color=#993300>(10/27/01 1:23:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ancients</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled softly.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ohi Ohi, I am actually entrigued by your curiosity, many would not care enough to ask such things.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked upwards towards the mountains that surrounded Scynthia, where the caves were. She then turned her gaze back to Kali.<br>
<br>
&quot;Ohi, not all amazons become ancients. You have to in ways prove to become one. Most royalty have already been or when in death will become. Those who dedicate themselves to the tribe and the Amazon Nation have that chance. Others, may be reincarnated. However, there are those Ancients that choose to come back as well.&quot; She coughed. &quot;My son, Wulf, was once an ancient.&quot;<br>
<br>
Realizes how awkward that must sound. A male amazon, a male ancient. <br>
<br>
&quot;I too held such a title in a past life.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxamznkali.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XAmznKali</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#993300>(10/28/01 7:34:33 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=www.homeotwn.aol.com/xamazonkalix WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ancients</span><hr size=1> &quot;Male Ancient? hm, akward. I thought sons of Amazons went to the Elysian Fields or something. You are a re-incarnation? Kool. May I ask who of? I understand if you wish not to.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 249<br> <font color=#993300>(10/28/01 10:04:46 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Past</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded at the mention of Wulf.<br>
<br>
&quot;Most sons usually have the same opportunity as other males in the world . . . but Wulf was different. He sacrificed his life to save the entire amazon nation. He was a chosen one.&quot;<br>
<br>
The subject of her past life was a bit touchy at times. When the athelfi usually found out, it shocked them, and sometimes scared them.<br>
<br>
&quot;My name was Samsara, of the Tretmolec Tribe.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=202.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showMessage?topicID=199.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=198.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=198.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=198.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=198.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm37">The Mythical Odyssey Forum<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitefrm32">The Mythical Odyssey<option value="amazonsunitefrm35">Amazon Nation Alliance<option value="amazonsunitefrm33">Character Descriptions<option value="amazonsunitesistersofthemiscr